body.query:
SELECT mu.mukey, mu.muname, c.cokey, c.compname, c.comppct_r, c.drainagecl, ch.hzdept_r, ch.hzdepb_r, ch.ph1to1h2o_r, ch.om_r, ch.awc_r, ch.sandtotal_r, ch.claytotal_r, mp.mupolygongeo.STAsText()
        FROM mupolygon mp INNER JOIN mapunit mu ON mu.mukey = mp.mukey INNER JOIN component c ON c.mukey = mu.mukey LEFT JOIN chorizon ch ON ch.cokey = c.cokey
        WHERE c.majcompflag = 'Yes' AND mp.mupolygongeo.STIntersects(geometry::STGeomFromText('POLYGON ((-98.23415786446807 32.959322081616676, -98.24727577903442 32.95944178128515, -98.2474663636282 32.95219778522704, -98.2271936426964 32.95299833683271, -98.22895853654724 32.95387888862075, -98.22914937845624 32.95519969573792, -98.23115273804162 32.95499957540889, -98.23253601575324 32.95632037042428, -98.23449171707628 32.95804136867211, -98.23430100638997 32.95900188964512, -98.23415786446807 32.959322081616676))', 4326)) = 1
        ORDER BY mu.mukey, c.cokey, ch.hzdept_r
